QuestData.Title: Muskpaw Ranch
QuestData.Description:
There's another Pandaren settlement out here, Muskpaw Ranch. I don't know if they're alright, what with everything that's been going on with the Yaungol invasion.
You've been so helpful - you should go check up on them, friend!
QuestData.LogDescription: Travel to Muskpaw Ranch in Kun-Lai Summit and speak with Lao Muskpaw.
